# Levellio environment variables (EXAMPLE — copy to .env and fill in).
# NEVER commit real secrets. .env is git-ignored.
#
# Expo exposes only EXPO_PUBLIC_* vars to the client bundle. Treat anything
# here as publicly readable in the app; keep true secrets on a server.

# --- AI layer (pluggable) ---
# Levellio ships NO developer-funded AI key. AI is optional; the app is fully
# usable without it. Cloud AI uses the USER'S OWN key, entered at runtime and
# stored only in the device secure keychain (expo-secure-store) — never here,
# never committed. On-device AI needs no key and no network.

# --- Firebase (planned auth + cloud sync) ---
# Placeholder app id: app.levellio.placeholder
EXPO_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_API_KEY=
EXPO_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=
EXPO_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=
EXPO_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_APP_ID=
